            color: highlight
                ? const Color(0xFFD4A24C)
                : const Color(0x33FFFFFF),
            width: 1.2,
          ),
        ),
        child: Center(
          child: asset != null
              ? Image.asset(asset, width: 22, height: 22)
              : Icon(icon, size: 20, color: Colors.white70),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }

